Atom seems to send the same structure as vscode
```json
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "workspace/didChangeConfiguration",
  "params": {
    "settings": {
      "metals": {
        "version": "0.4.0-SNAPSHOT",
        "javaArgs": [
          "-XX:+UseG1GC",
          "-XX:+UseStringDeduplication",
          "-Xss4m",
          "-Xms1G",
          "-Xmx4G"
        ]
      }
    }
  }
}
```
